203975681\"}],\"created_at\":\"2021-05-06T19:34:36.000Z\",\"text\":\"Providers made sense by dialoguing w/ patients, interacting w/ patients in their homes, &amp; through building relationships w/ patients. \\n\\n#HealthComm #healthcare #CommTwitter https://t.co/8GPf1q1aeY\",\"source\":\"Twitter Web App\",\"possibly_sensitive\":false,\"attachments\":{\"media_keys\":[\"3_1390389344259780613\"]},\"in_reply_to_user_id\":\"3291438365\",\"lang\":\"en\"},{\"id\":\"1390389242203975681\",\"author_id\":\"3291438365\",\"conversation_id\":\"1390388622692601860\",\"public_metrics\":{\"retweet_count\":0,\"reply_count\":1,\"like_count\":0,\"quote_count\":0},\"entities\":{\"hashtags\":[{\"start\":255,\"end\":266,\"tag\":\"HealthComm\"},{\"start\":267,\"end\":278,\"tag\":\"healthcare\"},{\"start\":279,\"end\":291,\"tag\":\"CommTwitter\"}],\"urls\":[{\"start\":292,\"end\":315,\"url\":\"https://t.co/dACBCmTizh\",\"expanded_url\":\"https://twitter.com/marleahdeank/status/1390389242203975681/photo/1\",\"display_url\":\"pic.twitter.com/dACBCmTizh\"}]},\"referenced_tweets\":[{\"type\":\"replied_to\",\"id\":\"1390388622692601860\"}],\"created_at\":\"2021-05-06T19:33:22.000Z\",\"text\":\"This article investigates how patients &amp; HCPs involved in a CCO communicatively make sense of medication taking. Patients made sense of medication taking as necessary &amp; important, as easy when supported, &amp; through building bonds w/ providers\\n\\n#HealthComm #healthcare #CommTwitter https://t.co/dACBCmTizh\",\"source\":\"Twitter Web App\",\"possibly_sensitive\":false,\"attachments\":{\"media_keys\":[\"3_1390388693798621186\"]},\"in_reply_to_user_id\":\"3291438365\",\"lang\":\"en\"},{\"entities\":{\"annotations\":[{\"start\":84,\"end\":98,\"probability\":0.9822,\"type\":\"Person\",\"normalized_text\":\"Brianna Cusanno\"},{\"start\":101,\"end\":111,\"probability\":0.9708,\"type\":\"Person\",\"normalized_text\":\"Vesta Silva\"}],\"mentions\":[{\"start\":71,\"end\":82,\"username\":\"USFComDept\",\"